quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,"Ka warran kan beeniya is abaal marinta (Aakhiro)."
  107,2,"Kaasu waa kan ula dhaqma agoonta si qallafsan.",footnotes:337758:2
  107,3,"Oo aan ku dhiirra gelin (dadka) quudinta miskiinka.",footnotes:337760:2
  107,4,"Waxaa hoog leh kuwaa tukada (munaafiqiinta ah),"
  107,5,"Ee ka dhoohan salaaddooda (ka dib dhiga waqtiyadooda)."
  107,6,"Kuwaasoo u fala (samaha) si loo arko."
  107,7,"U diida (dadka) maacuunta (waxyaalaha yar yar ee laysugu kaalmeeyo, zako iyo sadaqo iyaga warkoodba daaye)."
